---
import Link from "@/components/ui/link.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<main class="relative grid lg:grid-cols-2 place-items-center pt-16 pb-12 md:pt-24 md:pb-28 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="py-6 md:order-2 hidden md:block relative w-full max-w-2xl">
    <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-2xl shadow-slate-200/70">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-rose-400"></span>
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-amber-400"></span>
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-slate-500">
          edgeever.app/workspace
        </div>
        <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-600">D1 + R2</div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid h-[440px] grid-cols-[150px_190px_1fr] bg-white text-sm text-slate-700">
        <aside class="border-r border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/70 p-4">
          <div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-slate-900">
            <span class="grid h-7 w-7 place-items-center rounded-md bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700">E</span>
            EdgeEver
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-xs font-medium">
            <div class="rounded-md bg-emerald-100 px-3 py-2 text-emerald-800">全部笔记</div>
            <div class="px-3 py-2 text-slate-500">收件箱</div>
            <div class="px-3 py-2 text-slate-500">项目资料</div>
            <div class="px-3 py-2 text-slate-500">迁移归档</div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8 rounded-md border border-emerald-200 bg-white p-3 text-xs text-slate-600">
            <div class="mb-1 font-semibold text-emerald-700">MCP 已启用</div>
            Agent 可读取授权笔记
          </div>
        </aside>

        <section class="border-r border-slate-200 p-4">
          <div class="mb-3 flex items-center justify-between">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">最近笔记</h3>
            <span class="text-xs text-slate-400">128</span>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <article class="rounded-md border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 p-3">
              <div class="mb-1 font-semibold text-slate-900">Cloudflare 部署记录</div>
              <p class="line-clamp-2 text-xs leading-5 text-slate-600">D1 migration、R2 bucket、Worker route...</p>
            </article>
            <article class="rounded-md border border-slate-200 p-3">
              <div class="mb-1 font-semibold text-slate-800">Evernote 迁移清单</div>
              <p class="line-clamp-2 text-xs leading-5 text-slate-500">ENEX 导入、图片压缩、标签整理...</p>
            </article>
            <article class="rounded-md border border-slate-200 p-3">
              <div class="mb-1 font-semibold text-slate-800">Agent 整理建议</div>
              <p class="line-clamp-2 text-xs leading-5 text-slate-500">通过 Remote MCP 汇总本周笔记...</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="p-5">
          <div class="mb-4 flex items-center justify-between border-b border-slate-100 pb-3">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-950">Cloudflare 部署记录</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">今天 17:29 · 已同步</p>
            </div>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-emerald-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-700">在线</span>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4 leading-7 text-slate-700">
            <p>EdgeEver 将笔记正文保存到 D1，图片和附件保存到 R2。前端、API 和静态资源由同一个 Worker 承载。</p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3">
              <div class="rounded-md bg-slate-50 p-3">
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">笔记</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">10万+</div>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-md bg-slate-50 p-3">
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">图片</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">R2</div>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-md bg-slate-50 p-3">
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">接口</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">MCP</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-md border border-slate-200 bg-slate-950 p-4 font-mono text-xs leading-6 text-emerald-300">
              <div>$ bun run deploy:doctor</div>
              <div>✓ D1 binding ready</div>
              <div>✓ R2 bucket ready</div>
              <div>✓ Worker route ready</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="md:order-1 relative z-10">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-brand-text bg-brand-soft border border-brand-border/40 rounded-full mb-6">
      <span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand animate-pulse"></span>
      开源、自托管、Cloudflare-native
    </div>
    
    <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 leading-tight">
      EdgeEver
      <span class="block mt-2 text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl text-slate-700">把经典印象笔记体验部署到自己的 Cloudflare</span>
    </h1>
    
    <h2 class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-700 mt-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="text-lg lg:text-xl font-normal text-slate-500">三栏笔记、开放数据、REST API、OpenAPI 与 Remote MCP</span>
    </h2>
    
    <p class="text-lg mt-6 text-slate-600 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
      EdgeEver 是一个现代笔记工作区：保留笔记本树、笔记列表、主编辑区的熟悉工作流，把笔记正文存入 Cloudflare D1，把图片和附件存入 R2。它提供富文本编辑、PWA、离线草稿队列、客户端图片压缩，并让 AI Agent 通过 MCP 读取和整理你的个人笔记。
    </p>
    
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
      <Link
        href="https://github.com/msh01/edgeever"
        target="_blank"
        class="flex gap-2 items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-brand/20 hover:shadow-brand/35 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02]"
        rel="noopener">
        <Icon class="text-white w-5 h-5" name="bx:bxl-github" />
        查看 GitHub 仓库
      </Link>
      <Link
        size="lg"
        style="outline"
        rel="noopener"
        href="https://demo.edgeever.org"
        class="flex gap-2 items-center justify-center hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors"
        target="_blank">
        <Icon class="text-slate-700 w-5 h-5" name="bx:bx-show" />
        打开在线演示
      </Link>
      <a
        rel="noopener"
        href="/timeline/ai-agent-deploy-cloudflare"
        class="flex gap-2 items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-slate-200 hover:border-slate-300 rounded-lg text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900 transition-all text-sm font-medium"
        >
        <Icon class="text-slate-600 w-5 h-5" name="bx:bxs-bot" />
        AI Agent 部署
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
